description:
http://KEXP.ORG and Vive Latino present Live on KEXP from Mexico City with La Bruja de Texcoco performing at El Desierto Casa Estudio. Recorded October 15, 2023.

Nostalgia 00:42
Tepari 07:21
Dxiña huiini’ (Dulcesito) 12:01
Puerta en playa 15:58

La Bruja de Texcoco - Vocals, Harp, Violin
Andrea Sarahi Martínez Corte - Bass
Arturo Martínez Siller -Drums, Cajon
Mónica Avelino Chico - Vocals

Live on KEXP in Mexico City is a partnership with Vive Latino celebrating its 25th anniversary with the support of Indie Rocks! Magazine.Recorded at El Desierto Casa Estudio in Desierto de Los Leones, Mexico
